  dialogue:
  - I see...
  - If ye want te come with, ye need te fetch some stuff fer me.
  - Got it.
  - Git me fishin' rod 'n' harpoon.
  - The rod's by the cabin...
  - ...'n' the harpoon's by the lighthouse.
  - Why a harpoon?
  - Won't feel safe without it.
  - Set 'em up somewheres on the boat when yer brin' 'em aboard.
  - Now git!
